    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Furniture designed to be erected and dissasembled easily and quickly, produced for officers to be taken on military campaign.  Despite these requirements, campaign furniture is typically luxurious and crafted from quality materials.</Note_Text>
